<plot>Joe (George O'Hanlon) and Alice (Phyllis Coates) buy a television set and, on some excuse or another, the neighbors begin to drop in, stay to watch television and raid Joe's refrigerator. To escape the turmoil, Joe leaves and goes to the movies, where he finds himself sitting between Doris Day and Gordon McRae.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503841</url></doc>
